Member resource guide

Protecting what's most important

We’ve grown from a small mutual auto insurance company, owned by policyholders who spent their days farming in Ohio, to one of the largest insurance and financial services companies in the world.

Today we still answer to our members, but we protect more than just cars and Ohio farmers. We’re a Fortune 100 company that offers a full range of insurance and financial services across the country. Including car, motorcycle, homeowners, pet, farm, life and commercial insurance. As well as annuities, mutual funds, retirement plans and specialty health services.

We’ve served generations. Protecting what’s most important. Let us do the same for you.
Have a business to protect? See what we offer for businesses.

While supplies last. Availability and eligibility vary, visit terms and conditions for program details. Limit one Echo Auto per qualifying household. Offer is non-transferable and valid from 09/25/2019 while supplies last, or through 09/24/2020, whichever comes sooner. Always use your Echo Auto safely and follow all applicable driving and device laws. The Echo Auto is given away by Nationwide and redeemed on Amazon.com. Amazon is not a sponsor of this promotion. Echo Auto uses your existing smartphone plan and the Alexa app for connectivity and other features. Carrier charges may apply. Always use your Echo Auto safely and follow all applicable driving and device use laws. Shipping charges and taxes may apply to the full value of discounted and free promotional items redeemed on Amazon.com. If the Echo Auto device is returned, your refund will equal the amount you paid for the device, subject to applicable refund policies. If you violate any of these terms, the offer will be invalid. Use of Echo Auto is subject to the terms found here.
